328
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:41,980
Akan kutunjukkan padamu!

329
00:21:44,130 --> 00:21:45,770
Bagus, tunjukkan padaku!

330
00:21:45,770 --> 00:21:48,200
Buat aku lebih terhibur!

331
00:21:51,870 --> 00:21:52,450
(Itulah ...)

332
